	<version>1.15-SNAPSHOT</version>

	<name>Maven DataPower Plugin</name>
	<description>
		This plugin provides goals for: - Generating DataPower configuration based on predefined templates and specified WSDL files. - Importing files to a
		DataPower device. - Importing a pre-generated configuration to a DataPower device.
	</description>
	
